title: Japanese Prime Minister Takaichi's ruling LDP set to secure supermajority in Lower House: NHK
summary_full: PM Takaichi's Liberal Democratic Party is likely to win between 274-328 seats in the Lower House, higher than the 233 seats needed for a majority, NHK says.
summary_public: PM Takaichi's Liberal Democratic Party is likely to win between 274-328 seats in the Lower House, higher than the 233 seats needed for a majority, NHK says.
